{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_520.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...hmm... Bell, this book is really difficult."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No whining. You technically are an alchemist, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x80,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Is there a particular part you don't understand?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I can just barely understand the introduction. Everything from Chapter 1 on is beyond me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "The introduction is just the prologue! So you basically can't understand any of it!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, it is a magic book, so I guess that's only natural... Okay! I'll teach you step by step..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "So, the first this part is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "And that's roughly it. Got it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, more or less... By the way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "This is your task, right?<CR>Is it okay for me to be doing this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "It's fiiine. We get to choose our tasks, so we're free to do anything!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "R-Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Really. Besides, I think it's pretty arrogant to try to solve everything all by yourself!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Isn't it impossible for one person to have full knowledge of all the innumerable truths of the world?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Even if she is the world's greatest witch..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "So, asking people for help is an excellent means of accomplishing things."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, I see. That sounds convincing...or maybe not."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Anyways, as long as this task is completed, the process of making it won't come into question. I think..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I-Is that so...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "As long as she doesn't find ou‐<CR>...I mean, nothing!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Whatever the case, this is my first step to becoming the greatest and best witch in the world."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "So let's work hard together! Okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Then, your name will go down in history..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "As the best friend of Wilbell, the Great Witch!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I-In history? That'll just make me bashful and embarrassed..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "There's no reason to be bashful.<CR>Let's proceed with our heads held high!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, o-okay."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Well, let's stop here for today.<CR>We still have a long way to go!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x19a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Let's continue this next time!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, I hope this is okay. I hope Bell doesn't get scolded for it later.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "(But the contents of this book are really interesting. I think I'd like to study it a bit more.)"
        }
    ]
}